241
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:15,780
♪In the days after parting♪

242
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:19,380
♪Shedding the innocence♪

243
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:24,259
♪Never realizing that you and I♪

244
00:11:24,260 --> 00:11:28,140
♪Are born adversaries♪

245
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:30,899
♪He once invaded in every possible way♪

246
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:33,020
♪Claiming my territory♪

247
00:11:33,140 --> 00:11:35,259
♪Easily giving promises♪

248
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:37,459
♪Treated as optional questions♪

249
00:11:37,460 --> 00:11:39,859
♪In this age not favored by fortune♪

250
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:41,619
♪A moment of joy♪

251
00:11:41,620 --> 00:11:45,780
♪Yet repeating the same old habits♪

252
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:48,099
♪Twisted and tangled
interpersonal relationships♪

253
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:50,300
♪Hidden melodies♪

254
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:52,579
♪Stories, as tradition goes♪

255
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:54,499
♪Rise and fall in sequence♪

256
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,579
♪I wait for you♪

257
00:11:55,580 --> 00:11:56,539
♪Endless anticipation♪

258
00:11:56,540 --> 00:11:58,899
♪Till the latest trend
grows out of season♪

259
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:00,899
♪Who gathers the shattered heart♪

260
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:03,099
♪Becoming an undisclosed ailment?♪

261
